Metadata.Title: Just buy a house
Metadata.Description: Solving homelessness problem in China by throwing money at it.I mean, there is no homeless problem in China.Coin kill tips:1. Equip any melee weapon (except briefcase) and lock on the target.2. Open inventory and hold Aim Button.3. Select Coin and when inventory disappears immediately press Fire Button. If done fast enough 47 will throw the coin like the melee weapon you were holding before and it will kill the target.
